@startuml
title Use-Case-Diagramm: Lade Spiel...
left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false

actor "Spieler" as Player
actor "Tester" as Tester
actor "Datenquelle" as DataSource

rectangle "System: Dokumentenorientierte Datenbank" as SystemBoundary {
  usecase "Spiel starten" as UC_Start
  usecase "Spielinhalte laden" as UC_LoadData
  usecase "Aufgaben bearbeiten" as UC_Play
  usecase "Feedback erhalten" as UC_Feedback
  usecase "Punkte/Fortschritt sehen" as UC_Progress
  usecase "Runde abschliessen" as UC_Finish
  usecase "Neu starten" as UC_Restart
  usecase "Spielablauf verifizieren" as UC_Verify
}

Player --> UC_Start
Player --> UC_Play
Player --> UC_Progress
Player --> UC_Finish
Player --> UC_Restart
DataSource --> UC_LoadData
Tester --> UC_Verify

UC_Start .> UC_LoadData : <<include>>
UC_Play .> UC_Feedback : <<include>>
UC_Play .> UC_Progress : <<include>>
UC_Finish .> UC_Progress : <<include>>
UC_Restart .> UC_Start : <<include>>
UC_Verify .> UC_Start : <<include>>
UC_Verify .> UC_Play : <<include>>

note bottom
Quelle: databases/Teil02 FIAE/database/Datenbanken & SQL/Dokumentenorientierte Datenbank
Dateien: 1 HTML, 1 JS, 1 CSS, 1 CJS
